<h1>Listing All Famous People's Twitter Link:</h1>

<h3>The first I have done: followed the RoR online guide and created the app without the crawler</h3>
<p>This is basically the CRUD of the Database.</p>
<p>You can play around those add, edit and delete operations.</p>

<p>Once you done with this section, <%= link_to 'click here to go to the crawler part', guides_path %></p>


<%= link_to 'New Twitter Celebrity', new_twitterlink_path %>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Link</th>
  </tr>
 
  <% @twitter.each do |t| %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= t.name %></td>
      <td><%= t.link %></td>
	<td><%= link_to 'Show', t %></td>
   	<td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_twitterlink_path(t) %></td>
	<td><%= link_to 'Delete', twitterlink_path(t),
                    method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'You cannot be sure!' } %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>
